name: anyhasher-main
description: 1. Create key pair in AWS. [https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/create-key-pairs.html](docs) 2. Get the public key. [https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AWSEC2/latest/UserGuide/describe-keys.html](docs) 3. Add both in repo config so they can be used in CI/CD.  ``` SSH_PRIVATE_KEY SSH_PUBLIC_KEY ```
